title: ETH v1 Update: Raise SWAP Collateral Factor
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral factor of $SWAP from 0% to 25%, with a collateral cap of $500k.
Proposal: https://forum.cream.finance/t/proposal-increase-swap-token-collateral-from-0-to-25/1855 
Rational: Trustswap is currently using crSWAP as the base asset to farm SWAP. The ETH v1 market has ~$1.7M of SWAP deposited. 

For: 
Raise Collateral Factor of SWAP (ETH v1) from 0% to 25% — with Collateral Cap of $500k. 
Against:
 Do nothing.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
